title: Piano Music of the Darmstadt School, v 1 (Schleiermacher) [FLAC]
description:
Piano Music of the Darmstadt School, Vol. 1

Steffen Schleiermacher - piano

MDG 613 1004-2

Schleiermacher's first volume of typically awesome performances of modern European piano music of the late 50s and early 60s.

Ripped with cdparanoia III 10.2 and encoded with FLAC 1.2.1. Enjoy and seed liberally.
